{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Media Capture and Streams API (Media Stream)","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Media_Capture_and_Streams_API","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Media_Capture_and_Streams_API\">Media Capture and Streams API</a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Guides</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Media_Capture_and_Streams_API/Constraints\">Capabilities, constraints, and settings</a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Media_Capture_and_Streams_API/Taking_still_photos\">Taking still photos with getUserMedia()</a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Interfaces</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/CanvasCaptureMediaStreamTrack\"><code>CanvasCaptureMediaStreamTrack</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MediaDevices\"><code>MediaDevices</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MediaStream\"><code>MediaStream</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack\"><code>MediaStreamTrack</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrackEvent\"><code>MediaStreamTrackEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackCapabilities\"><code>MediaTrackCapabilities</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackConstraints\"><code>MediaTrackConstraints</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSettings\"><code>MediaTrackSettings</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints\"><code>MediaTrackSupportedConstraints</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/VideoStreamTrack\"><code>VideoStreamTrack</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Navigator/mediaDevices\"><code>Navigator.mediaDevices</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/captureStream\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.captureStream()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MediaDevices/getUserMedia\"><code>MediaDevices.getUserMedia()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/ended_event\"><code>HTMLMediaElement</code>: <code>ended</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/ratechange_event\"><code>HTMLMediaElement</code>: <code>ratechange</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>該<strong>媒體捕獲和流</strong>API，通常被稱為<strong>媒體流 API</strong>或者乾脆<strong>MediaStream API</strong>，是關係到一個 API<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/WebRTC_API\">的 WebRTC</a>提供流式音頻和視頻數據的支持。它提供了用於處理流及其組成軌道的接口和方法，與數據格式關聯的約束，異步使用數據時的成功和錯誤回調以及在此過程中觸發的事件。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"概念和用法","title":"概念和用法","isH3":false,"content":"<p>該 API 基於<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStream\"><code>MediaStream</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>對象的操作，該對象代表與音頻或視頻相關的數據流。請參閱“<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Media_Capture_and_Streams_API/Taking_still_photos#get_the_video\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">獲取視頻”中 (en-US)</a>的示例。</p>\n<p>A <code>MediaStream</code> consists of zero or more <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack\"><code>MediaStreamTrack</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> objects, representing various audio or video <strong>tracks</strong>. Each <code>MediaStreamTrack</code> may have one or more <strong>channels</strong>. The channel represents the smallest unit of a media stream, such as an audio signal associated with a given speaker, like <em>left</em> or <em>right</em> in a stereo audio track.</p>\n<p><code>MediaStream</code> objects have a single <strong>input</strong> and a single <strong>output</strong>. A <code>MediaStream</code> object generated by <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaDevices/getUserMedia\"><code>getUserMedia()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> is called <em>local</em>, and has as its source input one of the user's cameras or microphones. A non-local <code>MediaStream</code> may be representing to a media element, like <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> or <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/audio\"><code>&lt;audio&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, a stream originating over the network, and obtained via the WebRTC <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCPeerConnection\"><code>RTCPeerConnection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> API, or a stream created using the <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Web_Audio_API\">Web Audio API</a> <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamAudioSourceNode\"><code>MediaStreamAudioSourceNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>\n<p>The output of the <code>MediaStream</code> object is linked to a <strong>consumer</strong>. It can be a media elements, like <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/audio\"><code>&lt;audio&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> or <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, the WebRTC <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCPeerConnection\"><code>RTCPeerConnection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> API or a <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Web_Audio_API\">Web Audio API</a> <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamAudioSourceNode\"><code>MediaStreamAudioSourceNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"interfaces","title":"Interfaces","isH3":false,"content":"<p>In these reference articles, you'll find the fundamental information you'll need to know about each of the interfaces that make up the Media Capture and Streams API.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BlobEvent\"><code>BlobEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasCaptureMediaStreamTrack\"><code>CanvasCaptureMediaStreamTrack</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/InputDeviceInfo\"><code>InputDeviceInfo</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>MediaDeviceKind</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaDeviceInfo\"><code>MediaDeviceInfo</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MediaDevices\"><code>MediaDevices</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStream\"><code>MediaStream</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaDevices/getUserMedia\"><code>MediaStreamConstraints</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamEvent\"><code>MediaStreamEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack\"><code>MediaStreamTrack</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrackEvent\"><code>MediaStreamTrackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>MediaTrackCapabilities</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackConstraints\"><code>MediaTrackConstraints</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSettings\"><code>MediaTrackSettings</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints\"><code>MediaTrackSupportedConstraints</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>NavigatorUserMedia</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>NavigatorUserMediaError</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OverconstrainedError\"><code>OverconstrainedError</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/URL\"><code>URL</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Early versions of the Media Capture and Streams API specification included separate <code>AudioStreamTrack</code> and <code>VideoStreamTrack</code> interfaces—each based upon <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack\"><code>MediaStreamTrack</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>—which represented streams of those types. These no longer exist, and you should update any existing code to instead use <code>MediaStreamTrack</code> directly.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"events","title":"Events","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/Reference/Events/addtrack\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">addtrack</a></code></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/ended_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">ended (en-US)</a></code></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/Reference/Events/muted\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">muted</a></code></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/Reference/Events/overconstrained\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">overconstrained</a></code></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/Reference/Events/removetrack\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">removetrack</a></code></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/Reference/Events/started\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">started</a></code></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/Reference/Events/unmuted\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">unmuted</a></code></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"guides_and_tutorials","title":"Guides and tutorials","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The articles below provide additional guidance and how-to information that will help you learn to use the API, and how to perform specific tasks that you may wish to handle.</p><p><strong>There are no subpages at this time.</strong></p>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.MediaStream","dataURL":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Media_Capture_and_Streams_API/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"也可以看看","title":"也可以看看","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/WebRTC_API\">WebRTC</a> -API 簡介頁</li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaDevices/getUserMedia\"><code>mediaDevices.getUserMedia()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Media_Capture_and_Streams_API/Taking_still_photos\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">使用 WebRTC 拍攝靜態照片 (en-US)</a>：有關使用<code>getUserMedia()</code>。</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"概念和用法","id":"概念和用法"},{"text":"Interfaces","id":"interfaces"},{"text":"Events","id":"events"},{"text":"Guides and tutorials","id":"guides_and_tutorials"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"也可以看看","id":"也可以看看"}],"summary":"該媒體捕獲和流API，通常被稱為媒體流 API或者乾脆MediaStream API，是關係到一個 API的 WebRTC提供流式音頻和視頻數據的支持。它提供了用於處理流及其組成軌道的接口和方法，與數據格式關聯的約束，異步使用數據時的成功和錯誤回調以及在此過程中觸發的事件。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Media Capture and Streams API (Media Stream)","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"API de MediaStream","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"API MediaStream","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Media Capture and Streams API (Media Streams)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Media Capture and Streams API (미디어 스트림)","locale":"ko","na